- **Agent Monitor** â€” Algorithm engine status tracking
- **API Health Panel** â€” External integration status

### Case Management
- **Inmate Profiles** â€” Comprehensive case information display
- **Sentence History** â€” Complete sentencing record with amendments
- **Parole Timeline** â€” Hearing schedules and outcome tracking
- **Document Management** â€” Legal document organization and retrieval
- **Transfer Records** â€” Facility movement history

### Compliance Monitoring
- **Regulatory Adherence Scoring** â€” Multi-factor compliance calculation
- **Audit Trail Generation** â€” Automated compliance documentation
- **Violation Detection** â€” Proactive issue identification
